# Phase 1 Rules — Canonical Core and Import Framework

## What This Phase Builds

- Canonical entity schemas for all 6 domains (Asset, Resident/Lease, Operations, Demand, Market, Assessment)
- File import framework with schema mapping and review queue
- First PM connectors (Yardi, RealPage, Entrata, AppFolio, ResMan adapters)
- CRM data ingestion
- Manual field form ingestion (Audit Data Set)
- Entity resolution and alias mapping
- Coverage metadata and source provenance tracking

## Prerequisites

Phase 0 must be complete: databases provisioned, object storage working, tenancy/auth functional, CI pipeline running.

