Before writing any code, read these documents:

1. `rbv2-project.mdc` — Master project rules
2. `Code_Patterns_Specification.md` — Exact code templates for all services, routes, repositories, exceptions, and tests. Follow every pattern exactly. Phase 0 code in `src/services/authz/` and `src/services/engagement/` is the reference implementation.
